<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lecture-n">lecture <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'lektʃə(r)/    美 /'lektʃər/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(尤指大学中的)讲座；讲课；演讲：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>attend / go to a lecture</strong>
听讲座</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>give / deliver a lecture on</strong> history 
作历史讲座</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>教训；训斥：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I know I should stop drinking — don't <strong>give</strong> me a <strong>lecture about</strong> it.
我知道我该戒酒，别教训我了。</p></div></div>